{"title":"水调歌头当代颂","authors":["袁晓园"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":11,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"水调歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头当代颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁晓园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩云捧日出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛会喜相传。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸有邓公运幄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左右集英贤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌握中国特色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"制定方针宏略，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史写新篇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创立新世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"科技要争先。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大开放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深改革，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快加鞭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"封建漫漫长夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愚昧几千年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"积习从今涤净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民智曜人间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万邦来访问，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈笑说当前。（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九八七年十一月四日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写于北京春蚕室"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：指赵紫阳答中外记者问之风度。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}